1
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:16,120
Young Master, this bracelet...

2
00:00:16,720 --> 00:00:17,920
It's my fault

3
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,690
for failing to protect Xin'er.

4
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:23,920
All these years,

5
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:27,000
what have I really been able to protect?

6
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:31,900
I couldn't protect my mother,

7
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:34,850
I couldn't protect Xin'er,

8
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:38,280
and I can't even protect myself.

9
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:40,280
You have done your best, Young Master.

10
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:42,560
That venomous woman has committed so many sins.

11
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:44,960
If you hadn't been maneuvering in secret all these years,

12
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:47,680
quietly burying those poor thin women who died unjustly

13
00:00:47,680 --> 00:00:49,400
and compensating their families,

14
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,600
how could our mansion

15
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,330
have ended up like this,

16
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,100
reduced to an empty shell?

17
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,760
To keep you in check, that venomous woman

18
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:57,760
forced Miss Xin'er to marry

19
00:00:57,760 --> 00:00:59,680
the little prince of Quantan as a concubine,

20
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:01,200
killed the guards we sent,

21
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:03,760
and planted spies around her.

22
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,480
It's truly despicable.

23
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:13,300
Xin'er is the only family I have left.

24
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,060
No matter the cost,

25
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:18,580
I want it restored to its original state.

26
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:21,960
Act covertly.

27
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,289
Yes, sir.

28
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:26,940
Where is the paper?

29
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:35,600
Lady Fang indeed hasn't read the words on it.

30
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,240
It seems Fang Zhuozhuo

31
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,680
is not Lady Li's person.

32
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:49,479
Now that all the viburnum flowers in Qiwu Garden are destroyed,

33
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:52,160
this is the only one left.

34
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,280
Miss, you're awake.

35
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:16,920
Granny.

36
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,360
Granny, where is the flower?

37
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:23,520
There was a fire in the private garden of Qiwu Garden last night.

38
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,520
I heard all the flowers were burned,

39
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,560
including the viburnum flowers.

40
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,560
But Granny,

41
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,380
I got the viburnum flower.

42
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:36,570
Who brought me back to the mansion?

43
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,560
Chu Shengyi?

44
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:40,400
Right.

45
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,600
You inhaled thick smoke

46
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,730
and fell into a coma.

47
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,960
It was the young master who saved you from the fire

48
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,160
and brought you back.

49
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,120
Chu Shengyi saved me.

50
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,600
Drink this medicine while it's hot.

51
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,760
The smoke hurt your lungs.

52
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,960
You need to rest well,

53
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:02,440
otherwise it will leave a lasting illness.

54
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,680
I brewed it myself, don't worry.

55
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,360
Since Chu Shengyi found me,

56
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,170
he could have handed me over to Lady Li.

57
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,920
Why did he risk saving me?

58
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,840
The viburnum flower.

59
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,960
The viburnum flower is in Chu Shengyi's hands.

60
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,520
All the viburnum flowers in Qiwu Garden are destroyed.

61
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:34,120
The one I picked is now the only one in the world.

62
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,680
Chu Shengyi

63
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:38,600
must have guessed my intention of marrying into the mansion as a substitute.

64
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,060
He wants to keep the flower

65
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,880
to force me to hand over Qingcheng.

66
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:43,280
Then,

67
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,560
it seems we can't leave.

68
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,740
Since he wants to make a deal with you,

69
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,240
does that mean he won't hurt you?

70
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,970
It's hard to say he won't want to kill me again.

71
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,880
Last time, I was accidentally saved

72
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,760
by Lady Li's birthday banquet.

73
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,640
Next time,

74
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:06,200
I might not be so lucky.

75
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:30,650
It seems Miss Fang really isn't Lady Li's person.

76
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,480
But it's just a flower.

77
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:33,820
To risk her life

78
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,560
for it?

79
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:53,200
Are you feeling better, my lady?

80
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,320
Thanks to you, I'm much better.

81
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:02,600
My lady, come and taste this Jiangling Shaochun wine.

82
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:05,640
A little osmanthus was added when it was sealed in the jar,

83
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:08,500
so it has a faint floral fragrance when you drink it.

84
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,800
Your wine

85
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,400
is naturally a fine vintage.

86
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:24,080
But I wonder if today's main course

87
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:26,680
is to be tasted or admired.

88
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,240
This Qiong flower is rare,

89
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,800
so naturally it cannot be eaten.

90
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,240
Of course it's for admiring.

91
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,120
The flower is indeed extremely beautiful.

92
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,800
But the way it was obtained was ungraceful,

93
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:40,040
ultimately tainted with dust,

94
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,880
and losing some of its charm.

95
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,200
A treasure covered in dust

96
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,360
also blinds the eyes of those with intentions.

97
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,890
Knowing it's a doomed fate,

98
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,840
yet still gambling on luck.

99
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,480
If one has intentions,

100
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,560
how could they rely only on luck?

101
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:53,880
It's just that

102
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:57,800
they ignored the villain watching the chess game from the sidelines,

103
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,640
letting him unexpectedly make a move.

104
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:01,300
If that person could succeed,

105
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,890
it only shows that the one playing the game

106
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,280
had some oversights.

107
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,600
Are you feeling unwell, my lady?

108
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,800
You poisoned the wine.

109
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,760
The wine is not poisoned,

110
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:18,960
but I can't guarantee

111
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,970
that your body isn't poisoned.

112
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,680
At the birthday banquet that day,

113
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,960
your face was flushed,

114
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,880
and your breathing was rapid.

115
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,080
I was quite worried,

116
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,560
but I didn't expect

117
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,960
it was because of this Qilin cactus spine.

118
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,159
And this wine

119
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:34,890
only triggers the remaining toxins in your body.

120
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,010
Do you know, my lady,

121
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:40,480
my mother's garden is full of blooming flowers,

122
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,800
but there are no cacti.

123
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,040
To steal the Qiong flower,

124
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:45,760
you not only feigned illness,

125
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,820
but even set a fire.

126
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:47,880
But do you know

127
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,800
because of this fire,

128
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,720
the entire Huben Guard was beaten with military sticks

129
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:53,450
and they are lying in the military camp right now.

130
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,840
Imagine,

131
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:01,080
if my mother knew you broke into the garden to steal the flower

132
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:03,400
and burned down her entire garden,

133
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,040
what would she think?

134
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,160
This is all your framing!

135
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,720
Since you used it,

136
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,880
you naturally have a wound on your body.

137
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,690
If you still refuse to confess,

138
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:18,280
I might have to find a way

139
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,200
to examine your body.

140
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,080
I

141
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,760
had no way out,

142
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,240
so I resorted to this.

143
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:33,320
I originally only wanted to burn a haystack as a diversion.

144
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:36,250
Who would have expected the wind to suddenly pick up?

145
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,500
So you admit it.

146
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,880
You risked your life to get this Qiong flower.

147
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:46,080
It shows that the Qiong flower

148
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:48,159
is very important to you, right?

149
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,480
The secret of transforming into rouge

150
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,140
must not be discovered by him.

151
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,800
It was my cousin's order.

152
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,930
I dared not disobey.

153
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:57,740
Qingcheng?

154
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,280
Since things have come to this,

155
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:04,080
I won't hide it from you anymore.

156
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:06,240
Actually, marrying in her place and taking the flower

157
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:08,370
were all tasks given to me by my cousin.

158
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:11,560
Why did Qingcheng want to take this Qiong flower?

159
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,890
Maybe for the Makeup Selection Ceremony.

160
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,100
As to what exactly,

161
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,240
how would a lowly flower slave like me know?

162
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,900
Where is Qingcheng right now?

163
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,000
I don't know.

164
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,000
Really, if I knew,

165
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,880
why would I have suffered so much

166
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,360
in your private dungeon that day?

167
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,240
Besides, your guards

168
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,600
should have already searched all of Kuizhou

169
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,860
and the back mountain.

170
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,809
Did you find Qingcheng?

171
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,320
Why don't you

172
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,770
give me the Qionghua first?

173
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,000
Maybe

174
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,800
my cousin will show up.

175
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,040
Young Master.

176
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:30,940
Zanghua Pavilion.

177
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,320
It should be here.

178
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:35,640
This wandering merchant really has a lot of rules.

179
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:38,500
I heard solving this riddle is only the first trial.

180
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:25,960
Huanbo offers a cup to the guest.

181
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:32,760
Sir,

182
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,170
you seek an item,

183
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:36,560
while the merchant seeks fate.

184
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:39,480
Sir, only by draining this cup

185
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,320
can you see the truth.

186
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,200
Now,

187
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:03,480
can you tell me?

188
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:40,440
Xin'er.

189
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,680
Madam Li specifically instructed us

190
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,920
to take good care of the little madam.

191
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:50,560
Let me go.

192
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:52,680
Don't let her starve and lose weight.

193
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:55,680
Don't neglect the noble lady from Kuizhou.

194
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,520
Pry her mouth open.

195
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:58,400
Feed her.

196
00:11:58,880 --> 00:11:59,800
Eat.

197
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,640
This blade has no hilt.

198
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,240
It hurts both others and yourself.

199
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,720
You must think it through.

200
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:28,920
Xin'er.

201
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,520
Xin'er.

202
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,040
Xin'er.

203
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:38,920
Xin'er.

204
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,720
Please don't take offense, sir.

205
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:56,760
The wandering merchant from the Western Regions set this rule.

206
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:59,040
He won't sell his treasures to those without true devotion.

207
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:01,360
Thus, he set up this pipe dream

208
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,520
so that you

209
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,080
could see your true heart.

210
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:15,960
Xin'er's pain

211
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:21,160
is probably deeper than this dream.

212
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,560
So,

213
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,400
I passed.

214
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:37,400
Naturally.

215
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:42,960
Sir,

216
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,600
when you go to the black market,

217
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,200
hang this item at your waist.

218
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,210
Upon hearing

219
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,900
the sound of the willow flute,

220
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:54,880
you will be able to see the person you want to see.

221
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,080
Thank you.

222
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:08,880
I feel that

223
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,800
I have an affinity with you.

224
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,280
I'd like to remind you,

225
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:16,370
this is the first trap set by the merchant.

226
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,800
As for what comes next,

227
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,880
I do not know.

228
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:23,090
So when you arrive at the black market,

229
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,720
you must

230
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,320
be extra careful.

231
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:31,120
Farewell.

